com.atakmap.android.routes.nav

Class RoutePanelViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.routes.nav.RoutePanelViewModel

  • public class RoutePanelViewModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for managing the state (e.g. speed, units, eta, etc.) for purposes of navigation. Note: This class is thread-safe.
